<p>Carrying a striped baby bag on her shoulder, Felicity looked relaxed and happy as she steered the pram during her relaxing mother-and-baby stroll.</p>

<p>It is not yet known when the actress gave birth. The baby's gender and name have also yet to be publicly revealed.</p>

<p>MailOnline has contacted a representative for Felicity Jones for comment. </p>

<p>Over the past several months, the British actress hadn't been seen out and about, likely because of the global COVID-19 pandemic. </p>

